====Verb====
{{en-verb|lash|es}}

# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To strike with a lash; to whip or scourge with a lash, or with something like one.
#: ''We lash the pupil, and defraud the ward.'' &mdash; [[w:John Dryden|John Dryden]]
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To strike forcibly and quickly, as with a lash; to beat, or beat upon, with a motion like that of a lash.
#: ''the whale lashes the sea with its tail.''
#: ''And big waves lash the frighted shores.'' &mdash; [[w:John Dryden|John Dryden]]
